{"comments":"TextAnimation — Selectors and targeting for typography animation.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nAnimation requires targeting specific elements at various granularities:\n- Block level (entire paragraph animates)\n- Line level (each line independently)\n- Word level (each word independently)\n- Character level (each character independently)\n- Control point level (individual bezier handles)\n\nSelectors compose to express complex targeting patterns like\n\"every 3rd character of words 2-5 in the first line\".\n\n## Stagger Patterns\n\nStagger patterns define how animation timing spreads across elements:\n- Left-to-right, right-to-left\n- Center-out, edges-in\n- Random with deterministic seed\n- Custom function\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Prelude (Eq, Ord, Show)\n- Schema.Typography.TextIndex (index types)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[142,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TextAnimation.purs","start":[142,3]},"title":"TargetBlock"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[143,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TextAnimation.purs","start":[143,3]},"title":"TargetLine"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[144,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TextAnimation.purs","start":[144,3]},"title":"TargetWord"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[145,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TextAnimation.purs","start":[145,3]},"title":"TargetCharacter"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[146,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/TextAnimation.purs","start":[146,3]},"title":"TargetContour"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"source